description: Introducing Korilla BBQ, the fiercest eats you'll find on the streets of the concrete jungle. What is a Korilla, you ask? It is nothing less than a Korean grillmasta serving up a complex combination of classic Korean recipes nestled within burritos or rice bowls like you've never had before.They're using only choice meats, organic veggies, and the highest quality ingredients available to construct their killer menu. Carnivores and vegetarians alike love this NY K-'Q, and all environmentalists can appreciate their green, eco-friendly operation.The Korilla founders faced trials by literal fire, and still managed to come out on top to serve you their famously great food!
name: Korilla BBQ
